00:37:54,174 --> 00:37:57,924
I don't know the exact size, but it's for an 8-year-old boy.

524
00:37:57,924 --> 00:38:00,454
He's a bit chubby.

525
00:38:00,454 --> 00:38:05,494
If you're looking for clothes for an 8-year-old, sizes 120 to 130 will fit well.

526
00:38:05,494 --> 00:38:10,514
But considering he'll keep growing, size 140 might be best.

527
00:38:15,274 --> 00:38:17,714
Do you have this in that size right now?

528
00:38:17,714 --> 00:38:20,684
Wait one second, please. I'll check in the back.

529
00:38:26,874 --> 00:38:32,674
There's always someone who loves you and hates you.

530
00:38:36,124 --> 00:38:40,774
That's something out of my control.

531
00:38:45,034 --> 00:38:50,614
But the hostile are hating you, and that's it.

532
00:38:51,364 --> 00:38:57,964
The one you love will make you sad because of your love.

533
00:39:01,574 --> 00:39:03,314
Stand up.

534
00:39:05,474 --> 00:39:11,004
All people who gave me deep sorrow

535
00:39:11,004 --> 00:39:15,714
were the people I loved the most.

536
00:39:20,994 --> 00:39:23,834
The degree of my sorrow

537
00:39:23,834 --> 00:39:27,794
was exactly equal to the size of my affection.

538
00:39:28,484 --> 00:39:34,694
So it makes me scared to love someone now.

539
00:39:40,004 --> 00:39:45,484
I don't want to create more sad situations.

540
00:40:10,334 --> 00:40:12,744
Why am I being so pretentious?

541
00:40:19,740 --> 00:40:25,150
♫ Yes, I know it won’t be forgotten ♫

542
00:40:25,150 --> 00:40:29,910
♫ During the dark days ♫

543
00:40:29,910 --> 00:40:35,280
♫ Even if there’s no road ahead ♫

544
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:39,220
♫ To the place your footsteps reach ♫

545
00:40:40,604 --> 00:40:42,564
Dae Beom!

546
00:40:44,324 --> 00:40:47,654
Dae Beom! Dae Beom?

547
00:40:47,654 --> 00:40:49,574
Yeo Reum.

548
00:40:52,754 --> 00:40:54,904
You were over there.

549
00:40:54,904 --> 00:40:57,434
What brings you here?

550
00:40:59,344 --> 00:41:01,234
Well, the thing is...

551
00:41:07,004 --> 00:41:09,344
I wanted to say...

552
00:41:09,344 --> 00:41:12,394
have a safe trip to Seoul and come back safely.

553
00:41:13,724 --> 00:41:15,154
Sorry?

554
00:41:17,164 --> 00:41:19,334
I'm saying,

555
00:41:20,434 --> 00:41:22,924
"Have a safe trip to Seoul"

556
00:41:22,924 --> 00:41:25,134
"and come back safely."

557
00:41:32,284 --> 00:41:34,544
Yes, I'll come back safely.

558
00:41:38,994 --> 00:41:40,734
Also...

559
00:41:42,634 --> 00:41:46,954
I haven't canceled the movie tickets.

560
00:41:51,894 --> 00:41:53,854
Wait, Yeo Reum.

561
00:41:55,244 --> 00:41:58,404
This is for you.

562
00:41:59,214 --> 00:42:00,844
What's this?

563
00:42:00,844 --> 00:42:02,524
It's sneakers.

564
00:42:02,524 --> 00:42:06,424
You said that yours were ripped.

565
00:42:06,424 --> 00:42:08,854
But I wasn't sure on shoe size.

566
00:42:10,664 --> 00:42:12,554
Oh, but your sneakers...

567
00:42:13,324 --> 00:42:15,314
are fine.

568
00:42:16,914 --> 00:42:18,864
You're right.

569
00:42:20,014 --> 00:42:23,054
They are somehow fine.

570
00:42:24,624 --> 00:42:28,754
Then run for me as well, until I come back.

571
00:42:30,224 --> 00:42:32,304
Okay, I will.

572
00:42:46,490 --> 00:42:51,860
♫  It's your season again  ♫

573
00:42:51,860 --> 00:42:55,430
♫ I'll follow you ♫

574
00:42:55,430 --> 00:43:00,030
It's a nice... summer.

575
00:43:02,190 --> 00:43:07,150
♫ We held hands back then ♫

576
00:43:22,734 --> 00:43:27,164
If you go to the end of the library on the left side,

577
00:43:27,164 --> 00:43:30,364
there's one more seat in that corner.

578
00:43:30,364 --> 00:43:33,894
That's my favorite seat.

579
00:43:43,044 --> 00:43:46,484
I can't believe he had this great spot all to himself.

580
00:43:55,334 --> 00:43:57,364
- Hello.
- Thank you so much for coming today.

581
00:43:57,364 --> 00:43:58,514
Of course, we should come.

582
00:43:58,514 --> 00:44:00,494
- Dae Beom, go inside first. I'll park the car.
- Okay.

583
00:44:00,494 --> 00:44:02,324
- You can find us on the third floor.
- Yes, please go ahead.

584
00:44:02,324 --> 00:44:04,604
Professor Lee is already upstairs. Let's go.

585
00:44:04,604 --> 00:44:08,984
Please don't be nervous and just tell it as it is.

586
00:44:21,804 --> 00:44:23,764
This is the place.

587
00:44:35,134 --> 00:44:39,034
I'm sorry to bring you into an uncomfortable place again.

588
00:44:39,944 --> 00:44:41,274
Then let's start.

589
00:44:41,274 --> 00:44:44,324
- Just leave it there!
- It's fine. Let me help.

590
00:44:44,324 --> 00:44:46,724
But where's Bom?

591
00:44:46,724 --> 00:44:49,684
I think she went to change her clothes.

592
00:44:49,684 --> 00:44:52,354
- Just put it down! I can clean up.
- It's all done.

593
00:44:52,354 --> 00:44:55,294
Oh, my goodness!

594
00:44:55,294 --> 00:44:56,794
Bom!

595
00:44:56,794 --> 00:44:58,664
Bye, I'll see you tomorrow.

596
00:44:58,664 --> 00:44:59,924
Bye, see you.

597
00:44:59,924 --> 00:45:03,044
Bye! It's an ice cream cake. Enjoy it with the other staff.

598
00:45:03,044 --> 00:45:05,704
Thank you for the cake!

599
00:45:05,704 --> 00:45:07,984
I told you not to do stuff for the owner lady.

600
00:45:07,984 --> 00:45:09,784
It only makes me tired.

601
00:45:09,784 --> 00:45:12,424
Why? She liked it.

602
00:45:13,664 --> 00:45:16,534
Why did you take something so expensive?

603
00:45:16,534 --> 00:45:19,184
If I buy her something nice, she'll like it.

604
00:45:19,184 --> 00:45:22,834
Do you even know how much I get paid in a day?

605
00:45:22,834 --> 00:45:25,714
I'm sorry. I'll get something cheaper next time—

606
00:45:25,714 --> 00:45:27,534
Hey, watch out!

607
00:45:27,534 --> 00:45:30,634
- You almost hit us!
- What craziness is that?

608
00:45:30,634 --> 00:45:32,344
Watch out!

609
00:45:32,344 --> 00:45:34,424
Who is that? Is it someone who fought with you?

610
00:45:34,424 --> 00:45:38,444
What? None of them have a motorcycle.

611
00:45:38,444 --> 00:45:40,344
Hey, be careful!

612
00:45:40,344 --> 00:45:42,974
Who are you? Do you want to die?

613
00:45:42,974 --> 00:45:44,814
- That person must be crazy!
- Wait, wait.

614
00:45:44,814 --> 00:45:46,044
Wait!

615
00:45:46,044 --> 00:45:48,174
Bom, run away!

616
00:45:59,114 --> 00:46:01,884
What? Hey, Dae Ho!

617
00:46:01,884 --> 00:46:04,124
Bom!

618
00:46:04,124 --> 00:46:06,694
- When did you get out of prison?
- I just got out.

619
00:46:06,694 --> 00:46:09,794
I visited your grandmother and heard you're here.

620
00:46:09,794 --> 00:46:12,334
You should tell me first of your return.

621
00:46:12,334 --> 00:46:13,914
How can you not tell me? Do you want to die?

622
00:46:13,914 --> 00:46:16,734
Wait, did you get taller?

623
00:46:16,734 --> 00:46:19,344
- What? Me?
- You were tiny before, but you're bigger.

624
00:46:19,344 --> 00:46:21,644
Hey, my height was the same since middle school.

625
00:46:21,644 --> 00:46:24,404
But you look like you lost weight.

626
00:46:24,404 --> 00:46:27,354
- I just worked out a little bit!
- Hey, stop!

627
00:46:27,354 --> 00:46:30,864
What's going on? Let go of her now!

628
00:46:34,754 --> 00:46:36,614
Who's this guy?

629
00:46:37,204 --> 00:46:38,514
Well, he is...

630
00:46:38,514 --> 00:46:41,384
It's obvious. I'm Bom's boyfriend.

631
00:46:45,284 --> 00:46:48,044
Wow, Kim Bom. A lot happened while I was away.

632
00:46:48,044 --> 00:46:50,824
So who the heck are you?

633
00:46:50,824 --> 00:46:53,604
He's my best friend. We've been friends since babies.

634
00:46:53,604 --> 00:46:56,164
- Your best friend?
- Yes.

635
00:46:56,164 --> 00:46:58,154
A guy is your best friend?

636
00:46:58,974 --> 00:47:02,234
Let's introduce ourselves later. Kim Bom.

637
00:47:02,234 --> 00:47:04,954
Hey! Seriously!

638
00:47:04,954 --> 00:47:06,794
Let's see each other often.

639
00:47:06,794 --> 00:47:08,944
Okay. See you.

640
00:47:08,944 --> 00:47:12,424
Also, your name was...

641
00:47:12,424 --> 00:47:14,154
It's Jae Hoon, Heo Jae Hoon.

642
00:47:14,154 --> 00:47:16,964
Right. It's good to meet you.

643
00:47:16,964 --> 00:47:19,174
- Get home safely.
- I'll get going.

644
00:47:19,174 --> 00:47:21,024
Bye!

645
00:47:22,074 --> 00:47:24,184
What's wrong with you?

646
00:47:27,589 --> 00:47:29,500
I told you, he's just a friend.

647
00:47:29,500 --> 00:47:32,332
How can you hug so much with just a friend?

648
00:47:32,332 --> 00:47:35,544
He's my very close friend, my best friend!

649
00:47:35,544 --> 00:47:38,584
Yes, you can come over today.

650
00:47:38,584 --> 00:47:41,194
Okay, I'll see you soon.

651
00:49:06,160 --> 00:49:11,700
♫ I was young when I thought that being a hero ♫

652
00:49:11,700 --> 00:49:17,400
♫ Put on a cape, take flight ♫

653
00:49:17,400 --> 00:49:23,110
♫ Like a fading Polaroid and my favorite childhood toy ♫

654
00:49:23,110 --> 00:49:25,674
♫ I'm filled with faith ♫

655
00:49:25,674 --> 00:49:28,714
[Summer Strike]

656
00:49:28,714 --> 00:49:32,714
Geun Ho was filmed running out of here. Did anything happen?

657
00:49:32,714 --> 00:49:36,654
You were going to say it, but I guess it didn't feel right.

658
00:49:36,654 --> 00:49:39,894
Grandma, it seems you are inside my heart.

659
00:49:39,894 --> 00:49:42,474
My grandma will trade us and have you as her granddaughter!

660
00:49:42,474 --> 00:49:44,484
You came here to rest.

661
00:49:44,484 --> 00:49:47,254
Can't you think of it as an adventure you had on vacation?

662
00:49:47,254 --> 00:49:50,044
Please keep it secret! I'm so sorry.

663
00:49:50,044 --> 00:49:53,984
Grandma? Where did she go with the lights off?
